# Communication Protocols

- **CAN** — DriveCore Protocol (DCP) v0.1; no new IDs without updating `docs/004` and source of truth.
- **STM32 ↔ ESP32** — **versioned binary** DCPI on SPI; **not JSON** on SPI.
- **Web UI** — JSON only on REST/WebSocket; ESP32 translates from binary `STATE_PUSH`.
- Every message: sender, rate/timeout, payload layout, scaling, stale-data behavior.
- Heartbeat ≠ full health; distinguish BOOT, RUN, DEGRADED, FAULT, LOST.

Refs: `docs/004_Communication_Protocol.md`, EDL-009, EDL-010, `firmware/shared/`.
